Package civitas.celestis.util.group

Interface Tuple<E>

Type Parameters:
E - The type of element this tuple holds
All Superinterfaces:
Collectable<E>, Group<E>, Iterable<E>, Listable<E>, Serializable, Transformable<E>
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayTuple, Decimal2, Decimal3, Decimal4, DecimalArrayVector, DecimalQuaternion, Pair, Quad, Triple
public interface Tuple<E> extends Group<E>, Listable<E>, Iterable<E>
A shallowly immutable group of objects. Tuples have a defined order between its elements, and thus are convertible to lists.
